      ],
      "source": "https://sevchamber.growthzonecms.com/oak-hill/"
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "text": "By the Civil War, Oak Hill had a salt works, part‑time stores, and the first orange groves had been planted.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        4,
        25
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 2",
