      "source": "https://sevchamber.growthzonecms.com/oak-hill/"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "Beautiful 19th‑century homes add to Oak Hill’s history‑rich surroundings.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        11
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 2"
      ],
      "source": "https://sevchamber.growthzonecms.com/oak-hill/"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "A section of the National Canaveral Seashore Park extends into Oak Hill, featuring the historic Seminole Rest site.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        12
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 2"
      ],
      "source": "https://sevchamber.growthzonecms.com/oak-hill/"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "text": "Tucked between the beautiful Indian River Lagoon and the open Florida sky, Oak Hill is a place where small‑town spirit, rich history, and natural beauty come together just right.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        8
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 1"
